Thanks to your feedback this version includes:

- New Nutrition Diary design
- New Meals section
- Drag n Drop between meals
- Copy Food Items between days
- Multi-select any food in your diary to create a meal
- Daily Summary Analytics

...And of course bug fixes & optimizations :) Thanks for being the best part of Trifecta, please keep those suggestions coming!

Improved Trifecta ME 90-Day Challenge functionality
Improved Trifecta ME 90-Day Challenge functionality

Welcome to the new TrifectaME Dashboard! We’ve been working around the clock on this new feature to help you better visualize your 90-Day Challenge progress. Included is the ability to see a week of food logs all in one convenient screen, as well as your ‘Before’ and ‘Progress’ photos. Additionally, we’ve added levels to climb as you log your challenge points, and to help with that, we’ve even added a few more ways to get points!
